ch lead to an\noutward centrifugal energy flow and an inward gravitation energy flow. The lost\nvacuum energy in the negative gravitation potential region has been removed to\nthe black hole surface to form a spherical Planckon shell with the thickness of\nPlanckon diameter so that energy conservation is guaranteed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 24 Dec 2012 03:59:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 17 Feb 2013 14:26:15 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 26 Sep 2014 01:25:36 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 28 Oct 2014 04:01:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-10-29"}
