ee field configuration is closer (but not equal) to that of the linear\nforce-free field configuration than a potential one. However, the small degree\nof similarity suggests that partial Taylor relaxation has occurred over a time\nscale of ~ 3-4 hours.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 24 Dec 2012 12:46:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-03-10"}
